Module brickGame
Package brickGame.Model.Interface

Interface BallPosition

All Known Implementing Classes:
BallModel
public interface BallPosition
The Ball interface is used to set and get the ball's coordinates. Classes implementing this interface will need to implement the setBallXCoordinate, getBallXCoordinate, setBallYCoordinate, and getBallYCoordinate methods.
